I tried to convert an int to string, but the following function
```
function automatic string itoa(int val);                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
    automatic string x;
    x.itoa(val);
    return x;
endfunction
```

gives this error ` Unsupported: Member call on non-enum object 'VARREF 'x'' which is a 'BASICDTYPE 'string''`

What can I do?
